				If Apple releases a 20in. widescreen display at a $1000 price-point, I'm gonna be robbin' banks like it's my job.<br />
				<div class="byline"><a href="http://www.devlogik.com/www/E3R_2/blog/2004/06/thank-gawd-for-student-discounts.php#108695637714482842" title="permanent link">#</a> posted by <a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/3571774">cless</a> @ 8:19 AM</div>
				<span class="item-control admin-800438703 pid-58544947"><a style="border:none;" href="http://www.blogger.com/delete-comment.do?blogID=6900590&postID=108695637714482842" title="Delete Comment" ><span class="delete-comment-icon">&nbsp;</span></a></span>
